data.description: Hard to find stepless ranch in sought after Cherokee Bluff school zone! Step inside this charming three bedroom ranch with an open floorplan. The living room features vaulted ceilings with plenty of room for family gatherings and newer bamboo flooring. The open kitchen overlooks the family room and features a ton of counter top space and island. The primary bedroom features soaring ceilings with a huge walk-in closet. The primary bath has a double vanity and separate soaking tub and walk in shower. Two spacious guest bedrooms are located on the opposite side of the house making this the perfect floor plan. Recently replaced windows throughout the entire home and new hvac system. Don't miss the completely fenced in back yard with a charming covered patio. Relax fireside and watch the game from your outdoor oasis. The backyard is completely fenced in and level--perfect for children to play or fur babies to roam. But wait, there's more! The property line extends past the fence line into the woods for more opportunities to explore and play or garden. Located in Georgian Acres, this neighborhood offers convenience to shopping, restaurants, and is conveniently located within minutes to I-85/985  NGMC, Lake Lanier, Road Atlanta, Braselton and so much more. Community offers a playground, walking trails, pond, and swimming pool.
